Adresáře
########

Primárně ukládáme pluginy do domovské složky ($HOME). Konkrétně do techto
adresářů:

* Pluginy: ~/.local/share/gedit/plugins/	(http://askubuntu.com/questions/61785/how-do-i-install-a-plugin-for-gedit-v3)
* Styly (themes): ~/.local/share/gtksourceview-3.0/styles/	(https://live.gnome.org/GtkSourceView/StyleSchemes)
* LangSpecs: ~/.local/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs	(https://live.gnome.org/Gedit/NewLanguage)
* MimeTypes: ~/.local/share/mime	(https://live.gnome.org/Gedit/NewLanguage)
